    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Reaping tools with metal hooks mounted on wooden handles of about 40 inches in length. These were grasped in the left hand to hold crops which were then cut with siths held in the right.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
